data.title: Requests for new languages/Wiktionary Iban
data.text:
Language Wikidata item Q33424 - item has currently the following values: Item about the language at Wikidata. It would normally include the Wikimedia language code, name of the language, etc. Please complete at Wikidata if needed. Enable uploads no Default is "no". Preferably, files should be uploaded to Commons.

If you want, you can enable local file uploading, either by any user ("yes") or by administrators only ("admin").

Notes: (1) This setting can be changed afterwards. The setting can only be "yes" or "admin" at approval if the test creates an Exemption Doctrine Policy (EDP) first. (2) Files on Commons can be used on all Wikis. (3) Uploading fair-use images is not allowed on Commons (more info). (4) Localisation to your language may be insufficient on Commons.
